### Why this works for your business:

* **Tap-to-Call Functionality:** The main buttons use the `tel:` protocol, meaning mobile users can call your dispatch team with one click.
* **Local SEO Built-in:** The meta tags and body text mention Summerlin, Henderson, and the Las Vegas Valley to help you rank locally.
* **Trust Design:** The high-contrast Navy and Gold design screams "Professional Service" rather than "Handyman."

